</paragraph>
<paragraph id="8BCE36F93C6DB769FF4CFA7876AEFA37" blockId="38.[178,1086,1481,1525]" pageId="38" pageNumber="651">
T y p u s m a t e r i a l: 
<typeStatus id="54CA885B3C6DB769FE48FA78765EFA1F" box="[438,529,1481,1501]" pageId="38" pageNumber="651">Holotypus</typeStatus>
(): 
<collectingCountry id="F36676693C6DB769FDB5FA7876FDFA1F" box="[587,690,1481,1501]" name="Costa Rica" pageId="38" pageNumber="651">Costa Rica</collectingCountry>
